  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This research investigates the use of autologous bone marrow stem cells in patients with
      spinal cord injury.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate autologous bone marrow stem cells transplantation as a
      safe and potentially beneficial treatment for patients with spinal cord injury.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
